dct_title_s: 1:100,000 Palestine / Compiled, drawn & reproduced by Survey of Palestine.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contour intervals at 25 meters and spot heights. Map shows three classes of roads, tracks, railways and stations, international and administrative boundaries, villages, places of worship, police stations, ruins, caves, and tombs. Map also shows land use divided between orchards, olives, forests, vegetation, sand, and marshes. Map is complete in 16 sheets. Princeton University Library Map Room has 6 sheets. Mahleket ha-medidot- Yisra'el.
